ActJobs and Economic Growth Act
Financial System Review Act
SubjectOrder Fixing the Day on which this Order is registered as the Day on which Certain Sections of the Act Come into Force
PrecisOrder fixing the day on which this order is registered as the day on which (1) sections 1894 to 2135 of the JOBS AND ECONOMIC GROWTH ACT, chapter 12 of the Statutes of Canada, 2010; and (2) sections 9 to 11 and 207 and subsection 217(2) of the FINANCIAL SYSTEM REVIEW ACT, chapter 5 of the Statutes of Canada, 2012, COME INTO FORCE.
